edu.mit.jwi.item
Interface IPointerType

All Known Implementing Classes:
WordnetPointerType
public interface IPointerType

Objects that implement this interface represent all possible types of pointers that are contained in the dictionary data resources. The easiest way to do this in Java 1.5.0 is to use an enum implementation.

1.5.0
Version:
